textfsm_template:
Value DNS_SERVER (\S+)
Value DNS_ADDRESS (\S+\#\d+)
Value DOMAIN_NAME (\S+)
Value IP_ADDRESS (\d{1,3}(?:\.\d{1,3}){3})

Start
  ^Server:\s+${DNS_SERVER}
  ^Address:\s+${DNS_ADDRESS}
  ^\s*Non-authoritative\s+answer:$$
  ^Name:\s+${DOMAIN_NAME}$$
  ^Address:\s+${IP_ADDRESS}$$ -> Record
